author=kaandikec
description=Tailscale 1.98.2 arm64 binaries, OFF by default. Toggle from statusbot (/tailscale on|off). Adaptive routing — daemon follows current default route (VPN if up, cellular if not). Source-based MASQUERADE — never touches VPN routing/iptables.
